message: "If you use CQ-Bench-SNUH, please cite it as below."

title: "CQ-Bench-SNUH: A CDM-Resident Executable-Reference Benchmark for Natural-Language OMOP CDM Cohort Queries"
type: dataset

authors:
  - family-names: "Jeon"
    given-names: "Sohyeon"
