    affiliation: "Vital Lab, Healthcare AI Institute, Seoul National University Hospital"
    orcid: "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-0048-7957"

repository-code: "https://github.com/sohyeonclaire/CQ-Bench-SNUH"
url: "https://github.com/ssoooj/CQ-Bench-SNUH"

abstract: "CQ-Bench-SNUH is a CDM-resident executable-reference benchmark for evaluating natural-language cohort definition systems over an OMOP CDM. Reference labels are deterministic cohort counts derived from OMOP concept slots and SQL templates, not chart-reviewed clinical gold standards."

keywords:
  - OMOP CDM
  - cohort definition
  - benchmark
  - natural language query
  - executable reference
  - synthetic data

